Function holo emon ekta jinish ja kichu data input ney , eder upore kichu operation kore and erpore
kichu ekta output return kore . Function ke ekta machine er sathe compare kora jay .

Recursion holo emon ekta function ja nijei nijeke call kore . Ei function call cholte thake jotokkhon
na kuno ekta base case meet kore . Base case e emon kichu condition lekha thake jar kaaj amra recursive
function ke call korar age thekei jani . Jemon factorial of 0 = 0! = 1 . First two value's of 
fibonacci numbers are 0 and 1 .

Programming e loop diye jei kaaj kora jay shobgula kaaj e recursion diye kora jay . 
Recursion er Time Complexity = No of function calls * Work done in each call . 
Recursion er Space Complexity = (Depth of the recursion Tree / Height of the call stack)
                                        * ( Memory occupied in each call ) .

Recursion er prottek ta call er jonno alada kore ekta memory allocate kora hoy call stack e . Proti ta
call e alada stack e joma hoy . Jokhon kuno ekta stack er kaaj kora sesh hoy tokhon ta er ager step e
kichu ekta return kore . Ar memory call stack theke oi recursive call er stack ta shore jay . Eivabe
jei recursive call ta pore call hoise sheita shobar age stack theke shore jay . Eivabe ekta ekta kore
stack er kaaj sesh hoye jei poth e oi stack e pouchese oi eki poth diye ferot ashar prokriya ke bole
Backtracking . Backtracking er khetre jei ongshe recursive call ta kora hoisilo tarpore jodi kuno kaaj
lekha thake taile oita age songhotito hoy . Erpore oi stack ta call stack theke removed hoy .

Memory te stack er ekta limit thake . Jodi oi limit theke beshi stack memory te eki sathe joma hoy 
tahole runtime error ba segmentation fault hobe stackoverflow er karone . Ar jodi nirdisto shomoy
er vitore shobgula call shomponno na hoy recursive call er tahole time limit exceeded hoye jay .

ll factorial(ll number){
    if(number==0) return 1 ; // This is the base case . Karon amra jani 0! = 1 .
    return number * factorial(number-1) ; // This is the recursive formula for calculating factorial .
}

Ekhan porjonto basic recursion er sathe porichoy koranu hoise . Recursion use koira Dynamic Programming
er 99% problem solve kore fela jay . Ar DP holo programming world e explore korar jonno best ekta topic .
Loop er bodole recursion keno use korbo ? Ashole recursion emon onek subidha dey ja loop dite pare na jokhon
case gula complex hoy . Recursion e kuno ekta kaaj er shobcheye chuto step ta amra thik vabe kore felle baki
kaaj ta korar jonne amra nijeder ei function er upore bissash rakhte pari je thikvabe ei kaaj gula kore dibe.
