Basic je fibonacci number er recursive function ta ache er complexity holo exponential . Er mul time complexity
holo (1.618^n) . Tobe calculation er subidharte complexity O(2^n) calculate kora hoy . Ei complexity komanur 
proyojon jokhon pore thik tokhoni recursion er scene e chole ashe Dp ba Dynamic Programming .


